source.name: 2007 Results: Atrazine Monitoring Program for Community Water Systems
source.description: Syngenta, a Swiss company that manufactures the weed-killer atrazine, has been monitoring about 150 vulnerable watersheds across the United States under an agreement with the Environmental Protection Agency since 2003. Atrazine levels are as provided by the EPA Office of Pesticide Programs.
